Definition: dense shrub of moist riverbanks and flood plains of the eastern United States having attractive fragrant foliage and dense racemes of dark purple flowers
Synonyms: bastard_indigo, Amorpha_fruticosa, amorpha, dense, shrub, of, moist, riverbanks, and, flood, plains, the, eastern, United, States, having, attractive, fragrant, foliage, racemes, dark, purple, flowers
Category: noun.plant
